Tech Roadmap – ImpactMatch

Phase 1 (0–3 months)
- Build MVP with Firebase auth + storage
- Implement 1-Click Apply (profile auto-save)
- Launch closed beta with pilot NGOs

Phase 2 (3–9 months)
- Add NGO dashboards + social sharing
- Skill/location-based matching
- Onboard more NGOs & communities

Phase 3 (9–24 months)
- AI-based volunteer matching engine
- Verified NGO profiles
- Partnerships with universities & corporates
- Launch Flutter-based mobile app
